Module info.picocli.codegen
Package picocli.codegen.annotation.processing

Interface ITypeMetaData

  • public interface ITypeMetaData
    Abstraction over annotation attributes that take a class (or array of classes) as their value. For example: @Command(defaultValueProvider = xxx.class)
    Since:
    4.0

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      TypeElement getTypeElement()
      Returns the TypeElement of the type mirror.
      TypeMirror getTypeMirror()
      Returns the TypeMirror of the value.
      boolean isDefault()
      Returns true if the annotated element did not have the annotation attribute.
